  <title>Gio.ActionGroup::action-added</title>
  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
connect('action-added', function (actionGroup, action_name: String, ): void);
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Signals that a new action was just added to the group.
This signal is emitted after the action has been added
and is now visible.</p>
  <p>Since 2.28</p>
<terms>
<item>
<title><code>actionGroup</code></title>
<p>instance of <link xref="Gio.ActionGroup"/> that is emitting the signal</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>action_name</code></title>
  <p>the name of the action in @action_group</p>
</item>
